##############################################


### busca todos os produtos
GET {{PRODUCT_ROUTE}}

### Busca produtos pelo id
GET {{PRODUCT_ROUTE}}/1

### Adiciona um produto
POST {{PRODUCT_ROUTE}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "product 1"
}

